last_episode_to_air.name: The Anniversary Show
last_episode_to_air.overview: It’s the 10th anniversary show, the big event they’ve been working for all season, and it doesn’t go as planned. Not all the writers are invited back, and Andy stumbles on an invaluable discovery. Joy learns the truth about her father.

name: There's... Johnny!
overview: A coming of age story is set in 1970s Los Angeles following the lives and challenges of Andy, a wide-eyed 19-year-old Nebraskan who stumbles his way into a job at The Tonight Show Starring Johnny Carson, and Joy, a young talent coordinator on the show, as they both try to find their way and prove themselves in this period of cultural and political upheaval.

episodes.name: Andy Goes to Hollywood
episodes.overview: Andy Klavin travels from his Nebraskan hometown to Burbank, California, where he stumbles into a job meeting a colorful cast of characters – the writers, the producer Fred DeCordova, and most importantly Joy, who’s unlike any woman he’s ever met.

episodes.name: Dog Day Afternoon
episodes.overview: Andy juggles confusing feelings for Joy, and when he’s given his first important task at work, one bad thing happens after another. Somehow Andy ends up on his feet, and in the process manages to give Joy the credit she so rarely gets.

episodes.name: Owed to Joy
episodes.overview: Joy argues for equal pay at work, while juggling her own personal family drama at home. The writers take Andy on an outing he’ll never forget, and Mitch tries to hide his inner demons. Joy tries to mold Andy into the man she thinks he can be.

episodes.name: Take Me to Church
episodes.overview: Freddie invites Andy to his church in Beverly Hills, but it goes very badly, and Joy talks to her therapist about a recent wedding weekend gone wrong. When Andy calls his parents in Nebraska with some good news, he ends up getting news about his brother.

episodes.name: The Drop
episodes.overview: Based on a true story, Johnny Carson finds himself entangled in an extortion plot. Authorities are brought in, and some suspect Andy of being the plot. Andy also bonds with Joy and Rasheed while getting high for the first time in his life.

episodes.name: The Getaway
episodes.overview: Joy and Andy take a much-needed weekend getaway at Angelo’s party house in Palm Springs, but no one can relax with all the secrets being spilled.
